pageTitle: DB Dome LED Bollard by Hadco | DB14-AAO12LE
textBeforeTable: DB LED Bollard available in three sizes features a die cast aluminum alloy housing and dome roof with thermoset polyester powdercoat finish in Black or Bronze.  Symmetric optical assembly.  Die cast aluminum louvers with underside painted with highly reflective white powdercoat. Tempered glass globe. DB14 is 14 inches high x 6 inch diameter. DB21 is 21 inches high x 6 inch diameter.  DB30 is 31.75 inches high x 6 inch diameter.  All sizes include one 12.5 watt 120 volt Phillips LED Endura LED 2700K medium base A19 lamp. Ballast assembly is mounted to an aluminum plate which is mounted inside the base.  Quick disconnects for easy installation and removal.  For installation tube is mounted to the base plate with three 5/16-18 flat head allen key stainless steel tamper resistant screws. 5 inch base diameter. ETL listed for wet locations.  DB Dome LED Bollard REVIEWS BRAND TECHNICAL OPTIONS DESCRIPTION Shown in: Black
